{"tid":1701863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三罷前夕 將軍堡餐廳炒工會主席","createTime":"2019-11-09T11:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:57:54.000Z","uid":171506,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"08360d7ca4f2aaacb9bc235ef78fb99a2acc8a56","tid":1701863,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://radicalhk.com/2019/11/09/fire-chef/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fradicalhk.com%2F2019%2F11%2F09%2Ffire-chef%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=51722fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://radicalhk.com/2019/11/09/fire-chef/</a>"},{"pid":"6cfb28b838bb4084c9bcc46caab976414edc4cd9","tid":1701863,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95246a0ef394afbbe2167d70b85155a5d73580f7","tid":1701863,"uid":71253,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"有冇黃餐廳請人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7270d858a26827c7fe5831de326cb081b6366f2b","tid":1701863,"uid":171506,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"【本網訊】香港廚師聯盟工會主席吳志輝（細輝），原本任職位於香港紗廠的將軍堡餐廳，今日傳出被炒消息，仲要簽保密協議。未罷工先炒工會主席，如同代政權出手嚇工友。<br />\n<br />\n細輝接受&laquo;基進報導&raquo;訪問時透露，星期二在廚房大佬口中得知，公司以生意不好為由，需要調整營業時間削減人手開支，最初說考慮解僱另一位資歷較淺的廚師。後來星期五時，突然他引述公司指，因為「有很多報導、身份敏感」為由，公司希望將細輝辭退。<br />\n<br />\n將軍堡餐廳昨晚與細輝處理好合約內的金錢和薪金，又要求他簽下保密協議。細輝指，自己是在脅迫下簽名，「你說，這樣有沒有法律效力？」<br />\n<br />\n細輝除了是工會主席，亦是8.31事件現場目擊者之一，多次公開講述當晚情況。對於公司在三罷前解僱自己，他認為是出於政治打壓。細輝自己在3月在招聘廣告一般途徑入職，雖然廚房大佬亦說希望留用自己，但公司和母公司「新匯江」本身「藍底」，其他餐廳亦會受制於警方不敢聘用他，憂慮未能找到其他工作：「後面還會很多人會給餐廳壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n在科大生被警方逼死後，香港市民正打算發動全面三罷抗爭，當中組工會更是不少群組的首要議程。今次餐廳先幫政權出手打壓，既是打壓工人，更是對三罷運動全面宣戰。"},{"pid":"7873eab4fccbea72f5ed50401e3282b40f5cd5a2","tid":1701863,"uid":171506,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"請各位杯葛，不要幫襯。"},{"pid":"eb44c8262ec55a0f11da10413a823542ec2f0cf1","tid":1701863,"uid":92448,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab3be881453b38610322c3445ad14a7a01be4ee","tid":1701863,"uid":67465,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"殺雞儆猴<br />\n黃店一定要幫手請佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時勢炒個黃絲工會主席<br />\n佢更係想生意更加差喇<br />\n<br />\n各位市民請順佢意  罷食將軍堡"},{"pid":"88f67761c9278ec040f10c4ee9db0fe75c7536c1","tid":1701863,"uid":250979,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"罷食將軍堡同新匯江"},{"pid":"da8074bacfcb52d6aba316a203fe34196ca1c819","tid":1701863,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3d8d25ad98ae2a8ca6a9b97fd59e9aaf8ed5dfb","tid":1701863,"uid":121001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"95246a0ef394afbbe2167d70b85155a5d73580f7","tid":1701863,"uid":71253,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"有冇黃餐廳請人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:08:41.000Z","msg":"唔止請人啦<br />\n日日排住隊食<br />\n開多間餐廳都仲得"},{"pid":"eb7ab256d74b4cb6e0a47b3dbf7b2a13d8c975f2","tid":1701863,"uid":37740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:09:27.000Z","msg":"換季啦 係時候轉下d擺設"},{"pid":"589964e7de27ed319a241c1437849fa02e08f964","tid":1701863,"uid":236646,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:09:34.000Z","msg":"呢d 低能市真係白痴，肯定無人幫襯，細輝真係好出力支持香港人。佢只係一個普通廚師，但咁肯發聲幫自己行業真係唔話得。"},{"pid":"ab7eda15aef72c5482df11b02e72b546d5cdd141","tid":1701863,"uid":141833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836fdf05efb301743c7d1ac7a7220b86bce7577c","tid":1701863,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借個位黎唔該<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府會成立獨立調查委員會咁又點？五大訴求係咩？下一句係咩？唔記得哂？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a7754d16e937cee3ac97eefa07fa79746fbcead","tid":1701863,"uid":269125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新匯江<br />\n將軍堡</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"481aa38d0406f63619561426bee0f2f889f2d337","tid":1701863,"uid":260883,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03062dc995a7bf5a727e7b6d99925107c3fb7461","tid":1701863,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"眾籌俾錢佢開餐廳"},{"pid":"558a742c4c8bbf13578e6fbe7d3ae1ecf43e5dfb","tid":1701863,"uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6a7754d16e937cee3ac97eefa07fa79746fbcead","tid":1701863,"uid":269125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新匯江<br />\n將軍堡</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"荔枝角商業區<br />\n一間長沙灣道<br />\n一間都係附近"},{"pid":"0e66453106ddf8fa319a990b6bf6777b154d6a75","tid":1701863,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c52178feaf8a6f23e427930460ccfe1bd66608bb","tid":1701863,"uid":276857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-0